(387, 1, '2016-03-01 15:35:48', '2016-03-01 10:05:48', 'Hi,\r\n\r\nI hope this reaches you well, \r\n\r\nWe would like to associate with your company and distribute your apps on App Bazaar - World&#039;s Fastest Growing Regional App Marketplace. Please find details about our company Indus OS and App Bazaar below:\r\n\r\nVision of Indus\r\n \r\nMicromax&#039;s commitment and their belief in Indus OS is evident when they decided to launch with highest selling device model series. Indus OS is shipped 70% of Micromax Devices,i.e., 20 Micromax Devices in India at present and 15 devices in the pipeline which will be rolled out in the next 6 months. \r\n\r\nWe began our operations in Bangladesh last month, initially tying up with Elite Mobile, Indus OS is shipped with 3 Elite Mobile devices currently. We have closed the deal with Symphony and are also in advanced negotiations with other OEM&#039;s.\r\n\r\nEmerging markets like Pakistan and Indonesia are on our radar and we plan to enter these markets very soon.\r\n\r\nWith our initial estimates, we will be doing 10 million units in the first year. We are also in discussion with other brands and expect them to sign soon. With our relationship with multiple brands, we expect to have 100 million smartphones running on Indus OS by end of 2018. \r\n\r\nAbout App Bazaar\r\n \r\nApp Bazaar is The World&#039;s Fastest Growing Regional App Marketplace. As per our analysis we had seen that App Bazaar is used thrice than Google Play by Indus OS consumers because of its regional content and easy to use. App Bazaar is currently available in 10 languages.\r\n \r\nTo simplify app payments, we have introduced Indias first carrier billing integrated payment gateway, which allows the users to purchase apps with their phone credit. Free sign ups available for developers on App Bazaar. \r\n\r\nWith localized content available for the regional markets and high consumer re-engagement. App Bazaar has a very good and fast growing catalogue of reg